{"id":"ilai","term":"Ilai","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>An Ahohite, one of David’s chief warriors (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:29\">1 Chr. 11:29</a>); called also Zalmon (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:28\">2 Sam. 23:28</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 11:29","2 Samuel 23:28"]}